com.camerontec.util.pool

Class PoolableReference<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.pool.PoolableReference<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The reference type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDoublyLinkable<PoolableReference<T>>, IReference<T>

    public final class PoolableReference<T>
extends Object
implements IReference<T>, IDoublyLinkable<PoolableReference<T>>
    Poolable reference class.

    This class is designed to be used in conjunction with IReferencePool and its implementations.

    This class is not thread safe.
